Class JSONMapFilterListenerLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fortify.util.rest.json.preprocessor.filter.JSONMapFilterListenerLogger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IJSONMapFilterListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FoDJSONMapFilterListenerLoggerApplication, FoDJSONMapFilterListenerLoggerRelease, SSCJSONMapFilterListenerLoggerApplicationVersion

    public class JSONMapFilterListenerLogger
extends Object
implements IJSONMapFilterListener
    This class allows for logging messages regarding JSONMap objects that are either included or excluded by AbstractJSONMapFilter instances.
    Author:
    Ruud Senden
